r:#333333\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What\r\npersonal data we collect and process</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">We collect your personal data when you use our\r\nServices, create a new smart commerce account, provide us with information via\r\na web form, add or update information in your smart commerce account,\r\nparticipate in online community discussions or otherwise interact with us. We\r\nalso collect personal data from other sources (such as other smart commerce,\r\ncorporate family members or credit agencies or bureaus).</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">In total, we collect the following personal\r\ndata:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">3.1&nbsp;Personal data you provide when using\r\nour Services or creating an smart commerce account</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n\r\n</p><ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\">\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Data that identifies you, such as your name, address,\r\n     telephone numbers or email addresses, your user name, or your VAT\r\n     identification number that you provide when setting up your smart commerce\r\n     account or at a later date, and additional identification data and tax\r\n     identification numbers that you provide when using our payment services as\r\n     a seller.</span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Data regarding bids, purchases, or sales that you\r\n     provide in a transaction.</span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Content that you share with other users through our\r\n     messaging tools (see filtering of messages sent via our messaging tools\r\n     under section on other important information regarding data protection for\r\n     more information).</span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Financial information (e.g. credit card and account\r\n     numbers, payment details) in connection with a transaction.</span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Shipping, billing, and other information you provide in\r\n     connection with the purchase or shipping of an item, as well as information\r\n     required for customs clearance (such as tax identification numbers or\r\n     other identification numbers) and relevant shipping information (such as\r\n     shipment numbers and tracking information) if shipped through one of our\r\n     programs.</span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">In some cases: age, gender, country of birth,\r\n     nationality, employment status, family status, interests and preferences.</span></li>\r\n    <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0in 0in 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">You may provide us with additional information through\r\n     a web form or by updating or adding information to your smart commerce\r\n     account, by participating in community discussions, member chats,\r\n     inquiries, dispute resolution, customer service calls recorded with your\r\n     consent, or if you contact us